<h1>Help & User Guide</h1>

<div class="section">
  <h2>🏠 Dashboard</h2>
  <p>The dashboard gives you a quick overview of the system. You can navigate to Customers, Items, and Bills.</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>👥 Customer Management</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To add a customer: Go to <b>Customers</b> &gt; <b>Add Customer</b>.</li>
    <li>To edit a customer: Click the ✏️ icon next to their name.</li>
    <li>To delete a customer: Click the 🗑️ icon.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>📦 Item Management</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Add, edit, or delete items from the <b>Items</b> tab.</li>
    <li>Each item has a name, price, and description.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>🧾 Billing</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To create a bill: Go to <b>Bills</b> &gt; <b>Create Bill</b>.</li>
    <li>Select the customer and choose one or more items.</li>
    <li>The total is automatically calculated based on quantity and price.</li>
    <li>Click <b>Save</b> to generate the bill.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>📋 Viewing Bills</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To see all bills: Go to <b>Bills</b> &gt; <b>All Bills</b>.</li>
    <li>Click <b>View</b> to see full bill with items and total.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

